title: Getting ready to record lessons live stream
author: Lets Build That App
description:
Here at LetsBuildThatApp, I'll do my best to teach you how to build working apps from the AppStore, i.e. YouTube, Facebook, FB Messenger, etc.  We go beyond making simple blog and calculator apps to explore how professionals create million dollar projects.

My name is Brian Voong, a professional instructor and developer living in San Francisco, 10 years of knowledge to spread

FAQ
Q1: Can you show us how to write an app using storyboard instead of code/programmatically?
A1: Short answer, most likely no.  Long answer: It is my goal to dispel the misconception that building out apps programmatically is difficult.  I go through exactly how to write out components in code and many have found it very enlightening. Be brave, follow along, and you'll be OK.

Website: https://www.letsbuildthatapp.com
Mentoring: https://www.codementor.io/bhlvoong
Twitter: https://twitter.com/buildthatapp
